OL,3,CFunding cuts affecting council
OL,4,Ctransport service threatens
OL,5,Cindependence
OL,7,FA man in Basingstoke, who relies on
OL,8,Fcommunity transport, has reacted to
OL,9,FHampshire County Council's decision to
OL,10,Fcut its funding of some services.
OL,12,FThe cabinet considered proposed
OL,13,Fchanged to 13 areas, in a bid to fill
OL,14,Fits budget gap, which is predicted to
OL,15,Fbe at least #175 million.
OL,17,FIt has decided to remove #587,000 of
OL,18,Fcouncil funding to its Passenger
OL,19,FTransport provision.
