OL,7,FThis will impact taxi-share services,
OL,8,Fsupported local bus services and other
OL,9,Fpassenger transport.
OL,11,FAmong its users is Tony Nicholls, who
OL,12,Frelies on a 'Dial-A-Ride' service to
OL,13,Ftake him from home in Basingstoke to
OL,14,Fhis day centre. He is blind and has
OL,15,Flearning difficulties.
