OL,7,FTony said: "It's the only public
OL,8,Ftransport that's door-to-door and
OL,9,Fbasically, it's from people's homes.
OL,10,FIf it was to be cut, then it would be
OL,11,Fbad for myself and everyone who relies
OL,12,Fon it.
OL,14,F"It would be difficult to get out for
OL,15,Fpeople like myself and others as well,
OL,16,Fwho cannot do that or get out of the
OL,17,Fhouse independently."
