OL,7,FThe Cabinet says it's agreed that a
OL,8,Freview should be taken to make sure
OL,9,Fthat social care service users "are
OL,10,Fnot adversely impacted".
OL,12,FLeader of Hampshire County Council,
OL,13,FCouncillor Nick Adams-King said: "We
OL,14,Fhave worked hard and given careful
OL,15,Fthought to the proposals put forward
OL,16,Fto help us address our future
OL,17,Ffinancial pressures.
