OL,7,F"...Now that formal decisions have
OL,8,Fbeen made on the savings proposals, we
OL,9,Fwill take them forward over the coming
OL,10,Fyear with a view to maximising the
OL,11,Fsavings that can be achieved by April
OL,12,F2025.
OL,14,F"We will of course ensure people using
OL,15,Fthese services and the wider public
OL,16,Fare made aware of changes well before
OL,17,Fthey are made and what the potential
OL,18,Fimpacts might be."
